<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Trang chủ - SubTracker</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/output.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-slate-50 font-sans antialiased text-gray-900">
    <%- include('layouts/header') %>

    <main
      class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 animate-fade-in-up"
    >
      <div
        class="bg-indigo-600 rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-10 mb-8 shadow-xl shadow-indigo-200 relative overflow-hidden"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-16 -mr-16 w-64 h-64 bg-white opacity-10 rounded-full blur-2xl"
        ></div>
        <div
          class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 -mb-16 -ml-16 w-48 h-48 bg-purple-500 opacity-20 rounded-full blur-xl"
        ></div>

        <div class="relative z-10">
          <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-2">
            Chào mừng trở lại! 👋
          </h1>
          <p class="text-indigo-100 text-lg max-w-2xl">
            Cùng kiểm tra xem tháng này chúng ta cần thanh toán những dịch vụ
            nào nhé. Kiểm soát chi tiêu thông minh hơn mỗi ngày.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6">
            <button
              class="bg-white text-indigo-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold shadow-md hover:shadow-lg hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-200 flex items-center"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 mr-2"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"
                ></path>
              </svg>
              Thêm dịch vụ mới
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div
          class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
        >
          <h3
            class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-1"
          >
            Tổng chi phí tháng này
          </h3>
          <div class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-800">1,250,000 ₫</div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
        >
          <h3
            class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-1"
          >
            Dịch vụ đang hoạt động
          </h3>
          <div class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-800">
            08 <span class="text-base font-normal text-gray-400">gói</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-red-100 bg-red-50 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
        >
          <h3
            class="text-red-500 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-1"
          >
            Sắp hết hạn (3 ngày tới)
          </h3>
          <div class="text-3xl font-black text-red-600 animate-pulse">
            02 <span class="text-base font-normal text-red-400">gói</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
